thread.title_full: Tungsten World reviewed by Stephanie Chen

author: Stephanie Chen
title: Stephanie Chen
text:
I had a incredibly difficult custom engraving rushed specifically for Valentines day. A custom order poem in elvish separate from the LOTR ring on the website.
Not only did the ring and box come in early. But customer service made sure they were perfect by answering questions and suggesting design possibilities straight away.
He loved it by the way. Thank you for all you've done to make this happen!
